{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-publication-index-js","path":"/en/dp/090/the-impact-of-ltv-policy-on-bank-lending-evidence-from-disaggregate-housing-loan-data/","result":{"data":{"meta":{"siteMetadata":{"collections":[{"collection":"abridged","title":"aBRIDGEd","subtitle":"Making Research Accessible","url":"/abridged/","placeholder":null},{"collection":"thaipublica","title":"เศรษฐศาสตร์เข้า \"ท่า\"","subtitle":"Making Research Make Sense","url":"/thaipublica/","placeholder":null},{"collection":"pierspectives","title":"PIERspectives","subtitle":"Making Research Comprehensible","url":"/pierspectives/","placeholder":"pierspectives"},{"collection":"dp","title":"Discussion Paper","subtitle":"Making Research Inaccessible","url":"/dp/","placeholder":"dp"},{"collection":"members","title":"Members","subtitle":"Making Research Possible","url":"/pier-research-network/","placeholder":null},{"collection":"announcements","title":"Announcements","subtitle":"Making Research Public","url":"/announcements/","placeholder":"announcements"},{"collection":"blog","title":"PIER Blog","subtitle":"Making Research Public","url":"/blog/","placeholder":"blog"},{"collection":"conferences","title":"Conferences","subtitle":"Making Research Big","url":"/conferences/","placeholder":"conferences"},{"collection":"workshops","title":"Workshops and Forums","subtitle":"Making Research Work","url":"/workshops/","placeholder":"seminars"},{"collection":"seminars","title":"PIER Economic Seminars","subtitle":"Making Research Better","url":"/seminars/","placeholder":"seminars"},{"collection":"exchange","title":"PIER Research Exchange","subtitle":"Making Research Exchangable","url":"/exchange/","placeholder":"seminars"}],"series":[{"series":"Industry Transformation","placeholder":"industry-transformation"},{"series":"Public Economics","placeholder":"public-economics"}]}},"mdx":{"body":"var _excluded = [\"components\"];\n\nfunction _extends() { _extends = Object.assign || function (target) { for (var i = 1; i < arguments.length; i++) { var source = arguments[i]; for (var key in source) { if (Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty.call(source, key)) { target[key] = source[key]; } } } return target; }; return _extends.apply(this, arguments); }\n\nfunction _objectWithoutProperties(source, excluded) { if (source == null) return {}; var target = _objectWithoutPropertiesLoose(source, excluded); var key, i; if (Object.getOwnPropertySymbols) { var sourceSymbolKeys = Object.getOwnPropertySymbols(source); for (i = 0; i < sourceSymbolKeys.length; i++) { key = sourceSymbolKeys[i]; if (excluded.indexOf(key) >= 0) continue; if (!Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable.call(source, key)) continue; target[key] = source[key]; } } return target; }\n\nfunction _objectWithoutPropertiesLoose(source, excluded) { if (source == null) return {}; var target = {}; var sourceKeys = Object.keys(source); var key, i; for (i = 0; i < sourceKeys.length; i++) { key = sourceKeys[i]; if (excluded.indexOf(key) >= 0) continue; target[key] = source[key]; } return target; }\n\n/* @jsxRuntime classic */\n\n/* @jsx mdx */\nvar _frontmatter = {\n  \"id\": \"090\",\n  \"title\": \"The Impact of LTV policy on Bank Lending: Evidence from Disaggregate Housing Loan Data\",\n  \"authors\": [\"Chantawit Tantasith\", \"Nasha Ananchotikul\", \"Chatlada Chotanakarn\", \"Vorada Limjaroenrat\", \"Runchana Pongsaparn\"],\n  \"date\": \"2018-07-09T00:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"pdf\": \"pier_dp_090.pdf\"\n};\nvar layoutProps = {\n  _frontmatter: _frontmatter\n};\nvar MDXLayout = \"wrapper\";\nreturn function MDXContent(_ref) {\n  var components = _ref.components,\n      props = _objectWithoutProperties(_ref, _excluded);\n\n  return mdx(MDXLayout, _extends({}, layoutProps, props, {\n    components: components,\n    mdxType: \"MDXLayout\"\n  }), mdx(\"p\", null, \"How did the Loan-to-Value (LTV) measures aimed at increasing resilience of the banking system affect banks\\u2019 lending? This paper utilizes bank-level and contract-level data of housing credit in Thailand spanning from 2004 to 2017, and applies the panel data and probit approaches in evaluating the impact of LTV measures introduced in 2009, 2011 and 2013 on the housing loans. We find that the LTV measures had an impact on banks\\u2019 risk-taking behavior in ways consistent with the policy\\u2019s objectives. The effects manifest in a reshaping of LTV distribution of the targeted loan sector rather than a credit growth slowdown at the bank level. In addition, the size of adjustment varies across different types of banks, with stronger response from large and small banks compared with medium banks. Overall, our results suggest that certain macroprudential policies can achieve target-specific outcome, but with differential impact across banks. Nevertheless, questions remain regarding the channels through which LTV measures impact bank lending and factors underlying diverging response among banks.\"));\n}\n;\nMDXContent.isMDXComponent = true;","fields":{"slug":"/dp/090/the-impact-of-ltv-policy-on-bank-lending-evidence-from-disaggregate-housing-loan-data/","collection":"dp","shorturl":"/dp/090/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"The Impact of LTV policy on Bank Lending: Evidence from Disaggregate Housing Loan Data","subtitle":null,"series":null,"authors":["Chantawit Tantasith","Nasha Ananchotikul","Chatlada Chotanakarn","Vorada Limjaroenrat","Runchana Pongsaparn"],"date":"2018-07-09T00:00:00.000Z","updated":null,"cover":null,"excerpt":null,"bibliography":null,"topics":null,"tags":null,"layout":null,"pdf":{"publicURL":"/static/3b7f2b7ca6a302540f3e6f313c9828c4/pier_dp_090.pdf"}},"authors":[{"frontmatter":{"memberid":"Chantawit Tantasith","title":"Chantawit Tantasith","org":"pier","email":"ChantawT@bot.or.th","image":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/2e7a03592f67f5f238805903b785534d/dd515/profile.jpg","srcSet":"/static/2e7a03592f67f5f238805903b785534d/6a